race.comment: TRUE CHANCE (4) loves it here on his home track, and he settled back early from a wide draw over 1400m here fresh up, and finished off strongly to grab fourth, just 2 lengths from the winner. He is unbeaten on this track over a mile and can have the last say this time. GOT LUCKY (5) missed the placings two runs ago and again last start when always well back over an unsuitable 1200m here 4 weeks ago. He is back out to a mile, and a form reversal is expected. Each way. WEST COAST WARRIOR (6) is a stablemate of the top pick who was unplaced when resuming over 1300m here nearly a month ago. He usually improves quickly with racing, and he has not missed a cheque in 5 starts over this trip on the track, so stick with him. HEAVENBENT (9) has raced her way into form and is part of the travelling South Australian stable of David Page. She is worth including in all top 4 combos again. DEBONNAIRE (2) will have no fitness concerns fourth up from a spell, and he is ready to try a mile. Each way.
